  ],
  "description": "The signature FLASH Storm recipe at full intensity: Noise src1 through resonant BP filter (proc1=BP, 1850 Hz, reso=0.78) creates the ionized air of a lightning strike. gestureMode=3 (Tide/Surge) means every note attack surges and every note release subsides like a wave. flashTrigger=0.75 arms the FLASH gesture for dramatic transient events. No src2 — pure noise, pure storm. proc2=HP (180 Hz) cuts the sub mud; proc3=Off. Aggression=0.72. Four mods: LFO->FilterCutoff (storm frequency sweeps, 0.45 Hz), Env->Volume (surge envelope), Velocity->FilterReso (strike force tightens the BP), Aftertouch->FXMix (pulls into the storm space). Chorus+Reverb for full storm atmosphere.",
